1
00:00:02,980 --> 00:00:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you got a search request 
for a runaway?</font>

2
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

3
00:00:07,450 --> 00:00:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep. That very day, right after you left.</font>

4
00:00:11,740 --> 00:00:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A gaudy lady showed up 
wanting us to find a runaway girl.</font>

5
00:00:16,310 --> 00:00:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So who was it?</font>

6
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Satils Francois.</font>

7
00:00:20,090 --> 00:00:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know Shoppe Francois 
in the East District?</font>

8
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the owner.</font>

9
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if Ink was from a wealthy family,</i></font>

10
00:00:28,890 --> 00:00:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>would she really run away dressed 
like she'd escaped an orphanage?</i></font>

11
00:00:33,390 --> 00:00:37,220
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}JOB REQUEST
SEARCH FOR MISSING CHILD</b></font>

12
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be thankful I found someone to take 
that runaway girl off your hands.</font>

13
00:00:39,010 --> 00:00:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Y'lla.</font>

14
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, why's it 
so quiet in here today?</font>

15
00:00:44,410 --> 00:00:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you're the only one who's showed up.</font>

16
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? That's unusual.</font>

17
00:00:51,730 --> 00:00:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because none of the others returned.</font>

18
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From where?</font>

19
00:00:56,130 --> 00:00:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you heard? 
Dein and Kahnis had a duel yesterday.</font>

20
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea. Who won?</font>

21
00:01:03,870 --> 00:01:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein, apparently.</font>

22
00:01:06,380 --> 00:01:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why apparently?</font>

23
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kahnis and his hangers-on never came back.</font>

24
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only Dein.</font>

25
00:01:17,810 --> 00:01:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he won by default.</font>

26
00:01:20,780 --> 00:01:22,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Only Dein remained,</i></font>

27
00:01:22,770 --> 00:01:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and none of the others returned?</i></font>

28
00:01:26,350 --> 00:01:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does that even mean?</i></font>

29
00:01:39,210 --> 00:01:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No entry past this point.</font>

30
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to get to the 
other side, take a detour.</font>

31
00:01:44,650 --> 00:01:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you let us through?</font>

32
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just trying to visit 
my brother on the other side.</font>

33
00:01:49,550 --> 00:01:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about it! 
Nobody can go through here.</font>

34
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?</font>

35
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there something in there 
you don't want us to see?</font>

36
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, what's that stench?</font>

37
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something smells rotten. 
Gotta be a corpse or something.</font>

38
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master?</font>

39
00:02:10,810 --> 00:02:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit.</font>

40
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy this fits me just right!</font>

41
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great.</font>

42
00:02:18,190 --> 00:02:21,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a similar one for Sara too, but...</font>

43
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's not coming today either?</font>

44
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must be busy with Church work.</font>

45
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

46
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm worried about her.</font>

47
00:04:01,970 --> 00:04:04,680
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}REALITY
TRUTH</b></font>

48
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,980
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}TRUTH AND REALITY</b></font>

49
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking for a girl named Sara. 
She should be here.</font>

50
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:12,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait...</font>

51
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know her?</font>

52
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen to her?</font>

53
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is she?</font>

54
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara was excommunicated yesterday.</font>

55
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On orders from the pope.</font>

56
00:04:29,290 --> 00:04:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was banished as a demon-worshiper.</font>

57
00:04:32,670 --> 00:04:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously, that's a lie. It's all a sham.</font>

58
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara would never do anything of the sort.</font>

59
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't know where she is.</font>

60
00:04:43,610 --> 00:04:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll be put on trial at this rate.</font>

61
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please tell me you're okay, Sara...</i></font>

62
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'd like to meet Ed and Jonny.</font>

63
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two aren't here anymore.</font>

64
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were transferred out 
yesterday morning.</font>

65
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yesterday?</font>

66
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so sudden.</font>

67
00:05:01,790 --> 00:05:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet they were disappeared.</font>

68
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed... Jonny...</font>

69
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara...</font>

70
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you all go?</font>

71
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara got excommunicated, 
and Ed and Jonny were transferred?</i></font>

72
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on here?</i></font>

73
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I bet Ottilie knows something.</i></font>

74
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

75
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ottilie isn't here right now.</font>

76
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, I'd like to ask you 
if you know where she went.</font>

77
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even you don't know, General Henriette?</font>

78
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The royal army does not enjoy 
the trust of His Majesty.</font>

79
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rather, even the Lieutenant General 
can be erased without hesitation</font>

80
00:05:53,860 --> 00:05:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if she is adjudged 
to have defied the Church.</font>

81
00:05:59,690 --> 00:06:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ottilie was saying she wanted 
to unmask the real Church.</font>

82
00:06:04,710 --> 00:06:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked her to. 
The responsibility is all mine.</font>

83
00:06:09,650 --> 00:06:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said something when I met her last.</font>

84
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll be able to come back 
with good news before long.</font>

85
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She probably had a lead of some sort.</font>

86
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How reckless of her.</font>

87
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's never changed. Not then, not now.</font>

88
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She always clung to me like my own shadow.</font>

89
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She even trained in the sword 
when it wasn't her forte.</font>

90
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I hadn't been general, 
I could've responded to her feelings.</font>

91
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara and Ottilie both suspected 
the Church of wrongdoing.</i></font>

92
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And knowing Ed and Jonny, they would've 
done anything to protect Sara.</i></font>

93
00:06:53,610 --> 00:06:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ultimately, I dragged them all 
into this mess.</i></font>

94
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all my fault, huh?</font>

95
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master... Master...</font>

96
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

97
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

98
00:07:16,050 --> 00:07:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit...</font>

99
00:07:18,550 --> 00:07:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all gone...</font>

100
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it's all my fault.</font>

101
00:07:24,970 --> 00:07:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so awful.</font>

102
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Milkit. 
I'm such a useless master.</font>

103
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Before Milkit even thought to comfort her,</i></font>

104
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>her body was already moving.</i></font>

105
00:07:40,260 --> 00:07:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

106
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

107
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit...</font>

108
00:07:51,090 --> 00:07:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

109
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've done nothing wrong.</font>

110
00:07:58,350 --> 00:08:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit... But...</font>

111
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ottilie, Sara, Ed, and Jonny—</font>

112
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">people who were good to me—
all got taken out by the Church.</font>

113
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Dein's probably involved in it all.</font>

114
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He really has it out for me.</font>

115
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They all got targeted because of me.</font>

116
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go on anymore.</font>

117
00:08:24,530 --> 00:08:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry... I'm so sorry, Milkit.</font>

118
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I'm such a useless master.</font>

119
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master.</font>

120
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never knew that cooking 
was such a joyful thing.</font>

121
00:08:41,930 --> 00:08:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nor did I know that doing the dishes, 
the laundry, and shopping could be so fun.</font>

122
00:08:48,330 --> 00:08:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only after I met you did everything 
in my life take on a whole new light.</font>

123
00:08:53,810 --> 00:08:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are the one who gave me everything.</font>

124
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't be rid of the 
toxin marring my face,</font>

125
00:09:01,130 --> 00:09:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't have come to love this brand,</font>

126
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I wouldn't be here right now 
if it weren't for you.</font>

127
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are my hero, Master!</font>

128
00:09:14,850 --> 00:09:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please, don't call yourself useless.</font>

129
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay... Thank you,</font>

130
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit.</font>

131
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just Sara, but Ottilie too?</font>

132
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think they learned something about 
the Church they weren't supposed to,</font>

133
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that was why...</font>

134
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, stop! I have to get a grip!</i></font>

135
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This Satils woman who's looking for Ink 
might be connected to the Church.</i></font>

136
00:09:52,370 --> 00:09:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to keep Ink safe.</i></font>

137
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,660
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}PAELLA
BROCCOLI AND TOMATO SALAD</b></font>

138
00:09:56,190 --> 00:09:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Flum. Is Sara not 
joining us tonight either?</font>

139
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink...</font>

140
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think it's about time 
you told us the truth?</font>

141
00:10:09,230 --> 00:10:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have amnesia—</font>

142
00:10:11,450 --> 00:10:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We already know that's a lie.</font>

143
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't lie to us anymore, Ink.</font>

144
00:10:18,070 --> 00:10:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I went to the Guild today,</font>

145
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found that someone who claims to be your
parent has a search request out for you.</font>

146
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! Mother would never look for me!</font>

147
00:10:29,610 --> 00:10:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother? Is that what you call Satils?</font>

148
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Milkit?</font>

149
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Pardon me.</font>

150
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine. I'm sorry.</font>

151
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink, tell us about this "Mother."</font>

152
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I tell them anything, 
I'll be sent back there.</i></font>

153
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to go back. 
I'll get scolded real bad.</i></font>

154
00:10:53,110 --> 00:10:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After all, I left without permission.</i></font>

155
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No...</i></font>

156
00:10:58,460 --> 00:10:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No!</i></font>

157
00:11:00,290 --> 00:11:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stay here!</i></font>

158
00:11:02,590 --> 00:11:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stay with them!</i></font>

159
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least tell us about 
your medicine, then.</font>

160
00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I'm not taking any.</font>

161
00:11:17,410 --> 00:11:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink has a heart defect.</font>

162
00:11:20,230 --> 00:11:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She needs medicine, 
but I've never seen her take any.</font>

163
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she's run out, her life's in danger.</font>

164
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother told me to take it every day.</font>

165
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the first time 
I've gone so long without taking it,</font>

166
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but nothing's wrong with me, Eterna.</font>

167
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

168
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for telling us, Ink.</font>

169
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you going to scold me?</font>

170
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. I'd rather respect your wishes.</font>

171
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Eterna.</font>

172
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I lied.</font>

173
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ink told us everything after that.</i></font>

174
00:12:07,610 --> 00:12:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're part of a family of seven, 
you're ten years old,</font>

175
00:12:10,660 --> 00:12:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you have four younger, 
non-blood-related siblings?</font>

176
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

177
00:12:14,530 --> 00:12:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were all of you made to take that drug?</font>

178
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I was told only I needed it, 
because I'm first-generation.</font>

179
00:12:22,430 --> 00:12:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"First-generation"?</font>

180
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. The rest can all talk to Papa.</font>

181
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did they not let you see him?</font>

182
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. They didn't let any of us.</font>

183
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the others can hear his voice.</font>

184
00:12:35,770 --> 00:12:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Telepathy?</font>

185
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They probably came to hear 
a voice as their powers grew.</font>

186
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't just a hallucination?</font>

187
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. They were all mean to me 
because I couldn't hear it.</font>

188
00:12:47,990 --> 00:12:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I only realized recently 
that they were being mean to me.</font>

189
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Flum, Eterna, Milkit, and Sara... 
You're all so nice and warm.</font>

190
00:12:58,090 --> 00:13:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean it. I was the only one 
they never took outside.</font>

191
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is my first time being outside 
and meeting people other than my family.</font>

192
00:13:09,690 --> 00:13:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink, thanks for telling us. 
It must've been painful.</font>

193
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

194
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, is it my fault that Sara's gone away?</font>

195
00:13:18,810 --> 00:13:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will she come back 
now that I've told the truth?</font>

196
00:13:21,650 --> 00:13:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, she'll be back.</font>

197
00:13:23,610 --> 00:13:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Ink.</font>

198
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness.</font>

199
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's eat.</font>

200
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

201
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Ink, why "Mother" and "Papa"?</font>

202
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that not what people out here say?</font>

203
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's usually either Mama and Papa 
or Mother and Father.</font>

204
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That, or we use names.</font>

205
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know Mother's name, 
but I do know Papa's.</font>

206
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's called Origin.</font>

207
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Origin...</font>

208
00:13:54,320 --> 00:14:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Assuming the supernatural being 
called Origin really did exist,</i></font>

209
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>why was it targeting her?</i></font>

210
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:02,730
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}PAY F0R Y0UR SINS FLUM APRIC0T</b></font>

211
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:06,820
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FLUM APRICOT</b></font>

212
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:06,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flum was besieged 
by a fear of the unknown.</i></font>

213
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Eterna? Having trouble sleeping?</font>

214
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was double-checking what to do 
if worst comes to worst.</font>

215
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this about Ink?</font>

216
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink's heart isn't beating.</font>

217
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

218
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Sheitoom.</font>

219
00:14:35,930 --> 00:14:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen Neigass around 
these past few days.</font>

220
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She visiting the kingdom again?</font>

221
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

222
00:14:42,170 --> 00:14:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She just got back from there. 
How devoted can you be?</font>

223
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must've found 
something of value there.</font>

224
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to see 
what she brings back this time.</font>

225
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I guess I'll go play with them 
a bit before she gets back.</font>

226
00:14:58,220 --> 00:15:01,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heroes' party? 
I hear another one left them.</font>

227
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Who?</font>

228
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The taciturn knight.</font>

229
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gadhio? Is that true?</font>

230
00:15:07,690 --> 00:15:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, there's only four of them now.</font>

231
00:15:12,710 --> 00:15:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her heart isn't beating?</i></font>

232
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I can do is leave 
Ink in Eterna's hands.</i></font>

233
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed and Jonny? Yeah, I saw them running 
toward the bridge. Seemed in a real hurry.</font>

234
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. They were with that blonde nun.</font>

235
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I got there late, 
and nobody was there.</font>

236
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It reeked of flesh 
somethin' awful, though.</font>

237
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara and those two came here?</i></font>

238
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So they got mixed up in Dein's duel?</i></font>

239
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

240
00:15:46,060 --> 00:15:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this...</font>

241
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Clearly signs of a battle, right?</font>

242
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're Mr. Leitch's little sister.</font>

243
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, Welcy.</font>

244
00:15:55,050 --> 00:15:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you looking for Sara?</font>

245
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know anything?</font>

246
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone who went to watch the duel 
went missing all of a sudden.</font>

247
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something big must've gone down for sure.</font>

248
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, the ground's been scratched up.</font>

249
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, and even the walls.</font>

250
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All slashes of different 
depths and widths...</font>

251
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meaning they weren't caused 
by the same blade.</font>

252
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somebody must've used magic.</font>

253
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very least, it wasn't Sara. 
She fights with a mace.</font>

254
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of battle could've caused this?</font>

255
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came here thinking I might 
find a lead on the Church,</font>

256
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I don't think I'll find anything else.</font>

257
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. You said you were trying to find
who was smuggling herbs to the Church.</font>

258
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I was able to identify the culprit.</font>

259
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who was it?</font>

260
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Satils Francois.</font>

261
00:16:50,330 --> 00:16:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

262
00:16:51,710 --> 00:16:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got no evidence to back it up yet, though.</font>

263
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I should go.</font>

264
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lady calling herself Ink's parent 
has connections to the Church?</font>

265
00:17:02,340 --> 00:17:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

266
00:17:04,300 --> 00:17:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Eterna...</font>

267
00:17:06,690 --> 00:17:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to teach me magic.</font>

268
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that came out of nowhere.</font>

269
00:17:13,010 --> 00:17:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she finds out where Ink is, 
she'll come to take her back.</font>

270
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows what she's plotting?</font>

271
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want the power to protect Milkit 
and all of you with my own hands.</font>

272
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum. Magic is all about visualization.</font>

273
00:17:28,170 --> 00:17:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Create a clear vision in your mind 
and project it onto the matter before you.</font>

274
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Picture it...</font>

275
00:17:36,910 --> 00:17:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you need only say the words 
that come naturally to mind.</font>

276
00:17:51,250 --> 00:17:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm beat.</font>

277
00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit.</font>

278
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go shopping now 
so that Flum can rest.</font>

279
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

280
00:18:18,190 --> 00:18:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya.</font>

281
00:18:20,950 --> 00:18:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long time no see,</font>

282
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">mummy girl.</font>

283
00:18:25,320 --> 00:18:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein.</font>

284
00:18:26,660 --> 00:18:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is Dein?</font>

285
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. And wow.</font>

286
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't think I'd find you 
cheating on your master</font>

287
00:18:32,620 --> 00:18:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the hero Eterna Rinebow 
of all people.</font>

288
00:18:36,170 --> 00:18:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut your mouth, scumbag. 
Why are you here?</font>

289
00:18:40,650 --> 00:18:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to know 
the secret behind the children?</font>

290
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The children?</font>

291
00:18:45,950 --> 00:18:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That girl Ink and her ilk, of course.</font>

292
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're monsters. Got those dark 
crystals embedded right in 'em.</font>

293
00:19:08,470 --> 00:19:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're housing one hell of a calamity!</font>

294
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! It's an emergency!</font>

295
00:19:21,450 --> 00:19:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Eterna...</font>

296
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Eterna?</font>

297
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's under attack by eyeballs—</font>

298
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you're sopping wet! What happened?</font>

299
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

300
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll catch a cold!</font>

301
00:19:32,190 --> 00:19:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a sec. Where are the towels...</font>

302
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

303
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit? Why'd you turn off the lights?</font>

304
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Milkit?</font>

305
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

306
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you?</font>

307
00:19:59,850 --> 00:20:01,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

308
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

309
00:20:06,130 --> 00:20:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit!</font>

310
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? What's going on?!</font>

311
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was just here!</font>

312
00:20:13,430 --> 00:20:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit!</font>

313
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd you go?</font>

314
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit!</font>

315
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit?</font>

316
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you?</font>

317
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit!</font>

318
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you go?</font>

319
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

320
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

321
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink?</font>

322
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink?</font>

323
00:21:58,130 --> 00:22:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... No...</font>

324
00:22:01,630 --> 00:22:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

325
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:10,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b></font>

326
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:15,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Subtitle Editing: Geoff Mazzolini

Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b></font>

327
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:20,280
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Quality Check: Riley Dalton

Translation Check: Rei Miyasaka</b></font>

328
00:23:37,690 --> 00:23:40,020
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}DEIN AND FLUM</b></font>

